00:00:33.959 --> 00:00:43.959
First three minutes are without sound.

00:02:56.667 --> 00:03:01.667
But as I told you there could be good conditionings.

00:03:01.875 --> 00:03:06.959
In the way, in the same way, you can have good habits

00:03:07.125 --> 00:03:10.417
If habits inhibit

00:03:10.625 --> 00:03:14.333
or obstruct your ascent,

00:03:16.166 --> 00:03:22.083
they also can help to stabilize you.

00:03:29.375 --> 00:03:33.375
The conditioning comes to you from the matter

00:03:33.792 --> 00:03:37.083
with which we are dealing every day.

00:03:38.250 --> 00:03:43.417
When a human being sees the matter, he aggresses it

00:03:43.667 --> 00:03:48.291
and he wants to use that matter for his own purpose.

00:03:48.834 --> 00:03:53.375
He changes the forms of the matter for his own purpose.

00:03:53.875 --> 00:03:57.166
He starts getting used to matter

00:03:58.792 --> 00:04:04.875
as comfort, or as a help or a guide in life.

00:04:06.375 --> 00:04:09.291
The more you start depending on matter,

00:04:09.583 --> 00:04:12.750
the more your spontaneity is finished,

00:04:13.041 --> 00:04:16.792
because you’re dealing with the dead.

00:04:19.625 --> 00:04:23.041
Matter, when it is dead, then only we deal with it.

00:04:23.375 --> 00:04:28.041
When it is living we are not so much bothered about it.

00:04:28.458 --> 00:04:33.333
So the deadness of that matter settles within us

00:04:33.542 --> 00:04:39.291
when we start using that matter for our purpose.

00:04:39.917 --> 00:04:44.500
But how are we to otherwise exist, is the question people can ask.

00:04:44.750 --> 00:04:48.917
If God has given us this material things and this matter to be used,

00:04:49.208 --> 00:04:51.999
are we not supposed to use them?

00:04:52.458 --> 00:04:57.709
And are we not supposed to enjoy them?

00:04:58.375 --> 00:05:02.000
But we don’t enjoy really..

00:05:02.417 --> 00:05:06.375
Before realization you cannot enjoy any matter.

00:05:07.250 --> 00:05:10.333
You can only form a habit

00:05:10.625 --> 00:05:14.750
and may become a slave of that matter, before realization.

00:05:15.083 --> 00:05:19.959
It’s a principle of, fundamental principle of economics

00:05:20.333 --> 00:05:23.709
that wants in general are never satiable.

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:27.083
Means today you want to buy something like a carpet.

00:05:27.375 --> 00:05:29.250
All right, you bought it.

00:05:29.458 --> 00:05:32.999
So now that carpet becomes a headache,

00:05:33.333 --> 00:05:36.500
because it’s your possession, you have to look after it.

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:39.583
You have to insure it, you have to worry about it

00:05:39.792 --> 00:05:43.500
that it doesn’t get spoiled, first of all.

00:05:44.041 --> 00:05:46.375
And secondly you really get

00:05:46.792 --> 00:05:50.208
into another mood of buying something else.

00:05:50.834 --> 00:05:53.041
Now you have bought the carpet, finished.

00:05:53.792 --> 00:05:55.125
Then you have to have something else,

00:05:55.333 --> 00:05:57.875
then you have to have s.th. else, then you have to have s.th. else.

00:05:58.041 --> 00:06:02.792
So it does not satiate you; it does not give you the joy.

00:06:04.709 --> 00:06:07.083
Matter can never give you joy.

00:06:07.417 --> 00:06:10.041
It’s the Spirit that gives you joy.

00:06:11.375 --> 00:06:13.083
And when the ascent takes place,

00:06:13.500 --> 00:06:17.583
when you become the Spirit, then matter takes

00:06:17.917 --> 00:06:19.999
another value system within ourselves;

00:06:20.500 --> 00:06:24.959
the value system of matter is very different.

00:06:25.834 --> 00:06:27.875
As I’m sure Jason must have told you

00:06:28.291 --> 00:06:30.041
that when you get your realization,

00:06:30.959 --> 00:06:34.458
then you start feeling the cool breeze in the hand.

00:06:38.041 --> 00:06:39.750
In relationship to matter

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:43.500
it’s very helpful to be a realized soul,

00:06:44.166 --> 00:06:48.417
because immediately you know

00:06:48.999 --> 00:06:52.417
what is good for you and what is bad for you.

00:06:52.709 --> 00:06:56.792
For example, you eat something that’s not good for you:

00:06:56.999 --> 00:06:59.959
Immediately you’ll lose your vibrations and will become hot.

00:07:00.417 --> 00:07:02.959
Even looking at it, it may happen.

00:07:03.375 --> 00:07:04.792
You want to sit on a chair

00:07:04.999 --> 00:07:09.000
on which somebody who is a very wrong type of a person has sat,

00:07:09.458 --> 00:07:12.667
immediately you’ll feel, “Oh, something wrong in this place.”

00:07:13.000 --> 00:07:17.625
With your vibrations, which is a definite thing, an absolute thing.

00:07:20.792 --> 00:07:23.875
And this conditioning can only be over –

00:07:24.083 --> 00:07:27.834
these habits can be overcome only if you become the Spirit,

00:07:28.083 --> 00:07:33.000
because Spirit is always dominated by the matter.

00:07:33.417 --> 00:07:37.999
And the Spirit has to overcome that domination of the matter.

00:07:39.667 --> 00:07:43.250
Actually, Spirit cannot be dominated by anything.

00:07:43.709 --> 00:07:46.125
But what I mean is that it is covered,

00:07:46.458 --> 00:07:51.083
like the sun can be covered with clouds.

00:07:51.667 --> 00:07:55.000
In the same way all our domination,

00:07:55.417 --> 00:08:02.041
or we can say all our enslavement of the matter,

00:08:02.417 --> 00:08:05.417
makes us dominate our Spirit in the sense that

00:08:05.625 --> 00:08:06.625
we cover it up.

00:08:06.959 --> 00:08:09.667
The clouds are there, we can’t see the Spirit. We can’t feel it.

00:08:09.875 --> 00:08:13.291
The spontaneity which is the beauty of the Spirit

00:08:13.500 --> 00:08:15.667
we do not feel in a person.

00:08:16.166 --> 00:08:18.542
So, in judging a person, what do we judge?

00:08:18.999 --> 00:08:21.917
How that person looks, what dress he’s wearing,

00:08:22.166 --> 00:08:24.959
how he walks, what are his formal ways,

00:08:25.125 --> 00:08:27.792
does he know how to say “Thank you”, “Sorry” or not, you see?

00:08:28.250 --> 00:08:29.999
All these things impress us very much.

00:08:30.041 --> 00:08:34.125
What sort of a car he has, what sort of a house.

00:08:34.583 --> 00:08:41.166
Maybe we may miss, we may miss a saint.

00:08:41.999 --> 00:08:43.959
We may miss Christ again

00:08:44.250 --> 00:08:47.166
because He was a carpenter’s son.

00:08:47.709 --> 00:08:50.542
How are we to know who is Christ?

00:08:50.999 --> 00:08:55.792
Is there any way of finding out who is Christ?

00:08:56.291 --> 00:08:58.750
Many people are now talking “Christ is going to come,

00:08:59.000 --> 00:09:00.333
He’s going to come on the television.”

00:09:00.583 --> 00:09:03.917
You can put up anyone there as Christ.

00:09:04.375 --> 00:09:06.500
How are we going to make it out?

00:09:06.917 --> 00:09:09.583
By His dress or by some sort of a thing they have done?

00:09:10.041 --> 00:09:14.291
Most of the paintings of Christ and most of His statues

00:09:14.458 --> 00:09:16.500
that I’ve seen are no where near Christ,

00:09:16.750 --> 00:09:18.375
no where near Christ, you see.

00:09:18.625 --> 00:09:22.041
They are horrid things. I don’t know what are they.

00:09:22.750 --> 00:09:25.875
So how will you make it out that this is Christ or not?

00:09:26.166 --> 00:09:28.542
Or this is some sort of a hokus pokus fellow

00:09:28.667 --> 00:09:32.417
or some sort of a person who has come just deliberately

00:09:32.667 --> 00:09:35.999
to delude us from reality.

00:09:36.667 --> 00:09:41.208
There is no way out, to find out

00:09:41.959 --> 00:09:43.792
what is the truth because

00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:47.583
we are so much used to material forms that we have.

00:09:47.834 --> 00:09:54.999
For example, our idea of art also is in the same way moulded.

00:09:56.250 --> 00:09:58.000
We like this kind of art.

00:09:58.375 --> 00:09:59.709
If you ask them, “Why?”

00:09:59.959 --> 00:10:04.000
“Because, you know, this has this kind of a thing – harmony”,

00:10:04.333 --> 00:10:07.000
or maybe, “this is more proportioned” and all that.

00:10:07.375 --> 00:10:10.458
But how do you know?”

00:10:10.667 --> 00:10:13.458
You know because you’ve read certain books or maybe

00:10:13.792 --> 00:10:19.500
that you have understood from somebody else

00:10:19.959 --> 00:10:22.583
that this is art, this is beautiful.

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:26.500
I mean, you brand something as beautiful, but is it really?

00:10:26.834 --> 00:10:29.166
If it is beauty, it should be Spirit,

00:10:29.750 --> 00:10:32.625
because Spirit is beauty and beauty is Spirit.

00:10:32.917 --> 00:10:36.208
So is it, is it beauty? How do you make out

00:10:36.625 --> 00:10:40.166
that this art is beautiful or not?

00:10:40.333 --> 00:10:44.166
For example, according to all normal ideas of womanhood,

00:10:44.333 --> 00:10:47.375
I don’t think Mona Lisa is a beautiful woman.

00:10:47.875 --> 00:10:50.792
I mean the way these days you see mosquito-like women

00:10:50.999 --> 00:10:52.417
are regarded as beautiful.

00:10:52.750 --> 00:10:54.959
So how they call Mona Lisa so beautiful?

00:10:55.333 --> 00:10:57.208
What’s in her?

00:10:57.834 --> 00:11:00.458
Thousands of people would be assembled to see that painting

00:11:00.583 --> 00:11:02.999
Why? What has that?

00:11:03.417 --> 00:11:07.500
Only vibrations will tell you that it emits vibrations.

00:11:07.959 --> 00:11:10.417
It appeals to your Spirit without your knowledge.

00:11:10.583 --> 00:11:13.166
You’re not aware of it. It appeals to your Spirit.

00:11:13.333 --> 00:11:18.709
That’s why universally that painting is appreciated.

00:11:19.500 --> 00:11:22.041
But when this conditioning becomes collective,

00:11:22.583 --> 00:11:25.583
any such conditioning becomes collective and you accept

00:11:25.750 --> 00:11:29.250
“This is the form that is beauty;

00:11:29.333 --> 00:11:31.250
this is the form that is reality;

00:11:31.458 --> 00:11:35.166
this is the form that is spontaneity”,

00:11:35.417 --> 00:11:38.083
then the confusion starts.

00:11:38.542 --> 00:11:41.375
The confusion starts at that point,

00:11:41.583 --> 00:11:43.875
when it becomes a collective thing.

00:11:45.125 --> 00:11:47.875
For example I met some people of some gurus.

00:11:48.875 --> 00:11:50.709
When I asked them,

00:11:51.000 --> 00:11:53.333
“What makes you think that your guru is truthful,

00:11:53.542 --> 00:11:54.709
what has he given?

00:11:54.999 --> 00:11:58.792
