00:11:58.999 --> 00:12:03.792
I don’t do it but it happens, it’s spontaneous.”

00:12:04.208 --> 00:12:08.291
And in My presence, the way his body was moving was so horrifying.

00:12:08.542 --> 00:12:11.709
