00:12:12.208 --> 00:12:13.917
and concern for such a person,

00:12:14.083 --> 00:12:15.709
that you can’t sit for five minutes straight …

00:12:16.000 --> 00:12:19.834
Woman: Excuse me, it wasn’t spontaneous, it was nervousness.

