From where do you come?

00:12:29.375 --> 00:12:30.417
Woman: Up the road.

00:12:30.792 --> 00:12:32.458
That’s it. Better go.

00:12:33.166 --> 00:12:35.417
Woman: Don’t worry. I am.

00:12:36.250 --> 00:12:40.625
Look at that. She’ll go to the pub now.

00:12:43.917 --> 00:12:46.375
Must try to understand the subtleties, you see?

00:12:46.709 --> 00:12:48.166
If you are confirmed with what -

00:12:48.417 --> 00:12:51.583
Now supposing somebody starts jumping in the thing

00:12:51.917 --> 00:12:54.208
and he say's, - as she says it’s true, nerves,

00:12:54.625 --> 00:12:58.500
that means you’re not in control of your nerves, isn’t it?

00:12:58.709 --> 00:13:00.333
Don’t you think so?

00:13:00.709 --> 00:13:02.750
You’re not in control, you have not controlled.

00:13:02.999 --> 00:13:07.834
Spontaneity is a thing which is not the thing that makes you a slave.

00:13:08.083 --> 00:13:09.709
This is the point I’m trying to bring.

00:13:10.291 --> 00:13:13.583
It doesn’t! It makes you a master.

00:13:13.625 --> 00:13:15.583
Spontaneity must make you a master

00:13:15.875 --> 00:13:17.959
and not a slave of anything.

00:13:18.458 --> 00:13:22.917
She must have come from TM because TM people jump like that.

00:13:23.542 --> 00:13:25.583
