That’s why they said that He died for our sins.

00:54:57.500 --> 00:54:59.834
He is described in the ancient Indian scriptures

00:55:00.041 --> 00:55:01.834
as Mahavishnu but you see

00:55:02.041 --> 00:55:05.750
when the missionaries went to India

00:55:05.959 --> 00:55:08.917
they gave a very wrong picture of Christ, absolutely wrong picture,

00:55:09.083 --> 00:55:12.709
so they were still expecting Mahavishnu to come in.

00:55:13.291 --> 00:55:14.583
And this is what it is.

00:55:14.834 --> 00:55:19.083
He’s supposed to be, according to missionaries,

00:55:19.291 --> 00:55:23.458
somebody who sort of converts people and all that nonsense. See?

00:55:24.542 --> 00:55:27.542
It’s not the real thing, that He is to be awakened within us.

00:55:27.792 --> 00:55:31.000
He said that. He said, “I have to be born within you.”

00:55:31.625 --> 00:55:32.750
And that is what it is.

00:55:33.000 --> 00:55:37.500
When Kundalini rises, She awakens that center within us

00:55:37.792 --> 00:55:41.083
and all our conditionings and egos are sucked in,

00:55:41.333 --> 00:55:42.917
a space is created

00:55:43.083 --> 00:55:46.291
here in the fontanel bone area through which the Kundalini comes in

00:55:46.500 --> 00:55:49.917
and you can feel the cool breeze from your head coming out.

00:55:50.291 --> 00:55:52.750
That’s what it is. And you feel it in your hands.

00:55:53.000 --> 00:55:56.250
It’s not just that you’re mad after someone, you see?

00:55:56.999 --> 00:55:58.500
It isn’t like that.

00:55:59.208 --> 00:56:02.709
It’s not that way, you see, nothing of that kind.

00:56:03.250 --> 00:56:09.417
You become a Self-respecting, normal, dignified personality

00:56:09.625 --> 00:56:13.750
of great Spiritual value, which you are.

00:56:14.458 --> 00:56:15.291
All right?

00:56:15.583 --> 00:56:20.250
So this is what faith is and what is blind faith is.

00:56:22.417 --> 00:56:23.792
Yes, My child.

00:56:24.458 --> 00:56:27.291
Man: It seems very difficult the concept that

00:56:27.709 --> 00:56:32.999
Self-realization doesn’t involve some personal effort.

00:56:33.458 --> 00:56:38.083
Can it really come to anybody in effect of how

00:56:38.583 --> 00:56:42.375
materialistic they are? Am I understanding this?

00:56:44.083 --> 00:56:48.333
Yes, it appears on the face of it very difficult

00:56:49.333 --> 00:56:53.041
and how people are materialistic is also true no doubt,

00:56:53.333 --> 00:56:57.500
but Spirit is much stronger than the matter.

00:56:57.999 --> 00:57:00.750
And when It has to express, it

00:57:01.375 --> 00:57:05.625
completely crushes all that and It comes.

00:57:05.917 --> 00:57:09.166
Now, we have here, most of you are English people I should say,

00:57:09.417 --> 00:57:12.500
westernized, very materialistic people they were,

00:57:12.959 --> 00:57:14.417
I should say, I mean living in that world,

00:57:14.625 --> 00:57:16.166
they may not have been that materialistic

00:57:16.417 --> 00:57:19.875
because if they are not seekers, they would not come to Me.

00:57:20.125 --> 00:57:22.834
But a new being has been born.

00:57:23.166 --> 00:57:27.959
If you look at an egg you feel, “Oh, what a hard stuff is this!”

00:57:28.417 --> 00:57:30.709
But if it is broken at the right moment,

00:57:31.208 --> 00:57:34.834
with the right understanding, it becomes a bird.

00:57:35.291 --> 00:57:37.333
Because a living process is all,

00:57:37.542 --> 00:57:40.417
only the last breakthrough has to take place.

00:57:40.792 --> 00:57:45.625
Apparently it looks difficult, but to Me it is not.

00:57:46.208 --> 00:57:48.750
Perhaps I know the job.

00:57:49.250 --> 00:57:50.583
All right?

00:57:54.667 --> 00:57:57.000
Yes, it looks … many people have said all kinds of things

00:57:57.208 --> 00:57:58.291
about Kundalini, also.

00:57:58.500 --> 00:58:00.625
I must say some books I have seen have horrified.

00:58:00.999 --> 00:58:02.709
You see if you don’t know the job, everything –

00:58:02.917 --> 00:58:05.875
supposing if somebody else doesn’t know how to drive a car, you see,

00:58:06.041 --> 00:58:07.417
and he gets into the car

00:58:07.625 --> 00:58:09.417
the way he’d describe it would be horrifying.

00:58:09.625 --> 00:58:13.375
You’d never get near a car, isn’t it? It’s like that.

00:58:13.583 --> 00:58:14.875
The one who is not authorized and

00:58:15.041 --> 00:58:17.875
does not know the job should not do it.

00:58:18.208 --> 00:58:21.834
But that’s what happens to you, that you become

00:58:22.291 --> 00:58:25.000
the Spirit, you become your own master

00:58:25.333 --> 00:58:29.500
and you become the master of this art – the master of this art!

00:58:29.709 --> 00:58:31.500
Yes, My child?

00:58:41.959 --> 00:58:46.083
I couldn't hear you?

00:58:47.041 --> 00:58:49.625
You mentioned hypnosis earlier and

00:58:49.875 --> 00:58:54.709
You also said that You regarded Yourself as a catalyst...

00:58:55.208 --> 00:58:59.291
Don’t You think that the hypnotist also regards himself as a catalyst?

00:58:59.625 --> 00:59:02.333
Yes, very true. Yes, yes, no doubt!

00:59:02.834 --> 00:59:06.166
Yes, yes that’s true, but the difference is this,

00:59:06.417 --> 00:59:09.875
that the hypnotist brings you under his power.

00:59:10.041 --> 00:59:14.792
He doesn’t give you any power or no new dimension to your awareness,

00:59:15.000 --> 00:59:17.999
you see? There’s a tremendous difference between the two.

00:59:18.208 --> 00:59:21.208
You see, you have got your own power within you.

00:59:21.417 --> 00:59:24.166
Say, for example, all right, your Spirit there.

00:59:24.375 --> 00:59:27.583
Now I’m a catalyst, you see, you can use a spoon

00:59:27.792 --> 00:59:32.625
for giving a poison or could use it for giving a nectar.

00:59:32.917 --> 00:59:34.125
All right?

00:59:34.333 --> 00:59:37.959
So if you give the nectar, then it’s a great thing;

00:59:38.125 --> 00:59:41.125
and if you give the poison, it’s horrible. It’s like that.

00:59:41.333 --> 00:59:44.500
Now the hypnotist uses hypnosis –

00:59:44.709 --> 00:59:47.333
how does he hypnotize is the point.

00:59:47.542 --> 00:59:50.583
What he does is to push you into your subconscious,

00:59:50.792 --> 00:59:54.208
into your collective subconscious where he overpowers you.

00:59:54.709 --> 00:59:55.959
You are under his power.

00:59:56.125 --> 00:59:59.208
He says, “You become like a child”, you become like a child.

00:59:59.417 --> 01:00:02.000
“You suck a little bottle”, you do it. What’s all this?

01:00:02.417 --> 01:00:04.208
But here you become

01:00:04.417 --> 01:00:08.417
the Spirit in the sense that you become collectively conscious.

01:00:08.875 --> 01:00:12.750
It’s no hypnosis because you yourself can feel it.

01:00:13.375 --> 01:00:16.917
Now, say example you take ten children who are realized souls.

01:00:17.125 --> 01:00:18.959
There are some children who are realized souls,

01:00:19.125 --> 01:00:21.083
even little children.

01:00:21.667 --> 01:00:23.166
And you take them near a person

01:00:23.375 --> 01:00:25.917
who is suffering from some trouble, all right?

01:00:26.125 --> 01:00:27.917
Now you tie up their eyes

01:00:28.083 --> 01:00:31.542
and ask them, “What’s the problem of this gentleman?”

01:00:31.750 --> 01:00:33.625
They will raise the same fingers,

01:00:33.834 --> 01:00:37.041
all of them will raise the same fingers, say "This is burning."

01:00:37.250 --> 01:00:39.625
You see, because the sensation you feel –

01:00:39.834 --> 01:00:43.917
of burning, of numbness or of cool breeze,

01:00:44.291 --> 01:00:49.125
a new awareness of a vibratory nature is born within you.

01:00:49.417 --> 01:00:50.500
Not with hypnosis.

01:00:50.709 --> 01:00:53.875
On the contrary, after hypnosis you feel so tired and finished

01:00:54.041 --> 01:00:58.291
as if somebody has been riding your horse.

01:00:59.000 --> 01:01:00.291
It’s just the other way round.

01:01:00.542 --> 01:01:03.542
And you start growing into you and understanding,

01:01:03.834 --> 01:01:07.208
you can cure people you understand what are the centers

01:01:07.542 --> 01:01:08.792
that are catching,

01:01:09.000 --> 01:01:12.417
you understand what are the centers of another person that are catching.

01:01:12.667 --> 01:01:15.375
In the beginning sometimes people have confusion, I've seen,

01:01:15.999 --> 01:01:18.792
that they don’t know whether these are my centers or your centers.

01:01:19.041 --> 01:01:21.959
But we have ways and methods by which you can discriminate.

01:01:22.500 --> 01:01:24.291
You can see which are your centers catching

01:01:24.500 --> 01:01:26.625
and which are the centers the other person catching.

01:01:26.875 --> 01:01:30.291
You also know how to get them all right,

01:01:30.583 --> 01:01:33.125
you also know how to give realization to others,

01:01:33.333 --> 01:01:36.999
and to empower them with their own powers.

01:01:37.625 --> 01:01:39.999
It’s just the opposite.

01:01:40.583 --> 01:01:43.041
But catalyst could be horrifying,

01:01:43.250 --> 01:01:47.417
and catalyst could be just heavenly.

01:01:52.875 --> 01:01:57.625
Question: Can a person selfrealize themselves

01:01:57.834 --> 01:01:59.458
through their own effort (...)?

01:01:59.959 --> 01:02:01.750
With their own effort?

01:02:03.041 --> 01:02:06.417
O, that I don’t think is possible, you see, because

01:02:06.625 --> 01:02:10.834
like a light which is enlightened can only enlighten another light.

01:02:11.583 --> 01:02:16.959
But what I’m saying, that even supposing like Buddha, you see,

01:02:17.166 --> 01:02:19.999
He got His realization when He was absolutely tired

01:02:20.166 --> 01:02:22.917
and He had to have it. Of course the Holy Ghost did that.

01:02:23.083 --> 01:02:24.834
He could not have done it on Him,

01:02:25.000 --> 01:02:28.458
but He got the realization there

01:02:28.667 --> 01:02:32.375
because it was a different circumstance which He had to live,

01:02:32.667 --> 01:02:34.208
He didn’t have to talk about God,

01:02:34.417 --> 01:02:36.375
He didn’t have to talk about the whole thing.

01:02:36.667 --> 01:02:40.750
Because people were so much engaged

01:02:40.959 --> 01:02:43.208
in talking of big things like God

01:02:43.500 --> 01:02:46.291
and about all kind of deities, this, that,

01:02:46.500 --> 01:02:47.999
there was a big confusion.

01:02:48.291 --> 01:02:50.500
And somebody was to be realized at that time

01:02:50.709 --> 01:02:52.583
who would just localize it and say,

01:02:52.792 --> 01:02:56.417
“Only Self-realization! Don’t talk of God or anything, forget it.”

01:02:56.625 --> 01:02:58.709
That’s why He got realization like that.

01:02:59.208 --> 01:03:01.750
But you cannot get realization just like that –

01:03:02.083 --> 01:03:05.834
only possession you can get. You cannot.

01:03:06.458 --> 01:03:09.208
Somebody who is an enlightened soul,

01:03:09.458 --> 01:03:12.959
such an enlightened soul doesn’t take money from you.

01:03:13.500 --> 01:03:16.542
Normally, you see, people don’t want to give you realization.

01:03:16.834 --> 01:03:19.166
Ninety-nine percent of those who are really realized,

01:03:19.375 --> 01:03:21.750
they will throw stones at you, they won’t have anything to do with you

01:03:21.959 --> 01:03:25.000
because their experiences of human beings are horrifying.

01:03:25.208 --> 01:03:27.375
If you go and talk to them, they’ll tell Me,

01:03:27.583 --> 01:03:29.709
they told Me that “Wait for twelve years.

01:03:30.000 --> 01:03:32.999
See, Mother, they will all finish You off,

01:03:33.166 --> 01:03:34.999
they’ll kill You, they’ll do this.”

01:03:35.417 --> 01:03:37.333
It’s very venturesome to deal with human beings

01:03:37.583 --> 01:03:41.166
because they’ll be very egoistical and they will never accept you.

01:03:41.500 --> 01:03:45.375
But if you take like this, like

01:03:47.417 --> 01:03:51.583
somebody who knows, is a help, isn’t it?

01:03:52.625 --> 01:03:56.999
And realization is not possible, is not possible

01:03:57.458 --> 01:04:01.041
to be done by yourself. It’s not possible.

01:04:01.417 --> 01:04:05.583
Because if a, say, a candle which is not enlightened

01:04:05.792 --> 01:04:07.542
wants to get itself enlightened,

01:04:07.750 --> 01:04:10.166
the light has to be brought, isn’t it?

01:04:10.792 --> 01:04:12.375
It’s so simple as that.

01:04:12.667 --> 01:04:15.417
But one should not feel bad about it, actually.

01:04:15.834 --> 01:04:18.583
See, I don’t know how to drive, somebody drove Me down here.

01:04:18.792 --> 01:04:22.792
I didn’t feel bad that he had to drive Me down, did I?

01:04:23.166 --> 01:04:25.291
And I only know one job. I don’t know many.

01:04:25.500 --> 01:04:27.458
Many jobs I don’t know, I don’t know how to operate bank,

01:04:27.667 --> 01:04:31.792
I don’t know how to write a check, I’m hopeless in many things.

01:04:32.083 --> 01:04:34.583
I don’t know how to open a can, maybe.

01:04:34.959 --> 01:04:37.750
But I know how to open the Kundalini.

01:04:37.959 --> 01:04:40.625
All right? So if I know one job, why should you mind?

01:04:40.834 --> 01:04:44.750
After all, we depend on each other for everything, isn't it?

01:04:45.250 --> 01:04:47.959
So why not, if I know the job, what’s the harm?

01:04:48.250 --> 01:04:50.875
And you will know, too.

01:04:51.500 --> 01:04:52.792
You will know, too.

01:04:53.000 --> 01:04:55.125
But it cannot be done by yourself.

01:04:55.750 --> 01:05:00.291
But actually in this you’re not obliged for anything.

01:05:03.083 --> 01:05:05.750
I just do it because I love it.

01:05:06.083 --> 01:05:08.417
It’s just emits, I don’t do anyway, I’m just flowing,

01:05:08.625 --> 01:05:13.709
I don’t know how it happens, just it’s flowing.

01:05:19.917 --> 01:05:21.792
I just love for love’s sake.

01:05:21.999 --> 01:05:24.166
Just, you can’t believe such a person can exist,

01:05:24.375 --> 01:05:27.291
but I do really, I am like that.

01:05:27.542 --> 01:05:28.750
Sometimes you might even,

01:05:28.959 --> 01:05:32.000
some of the Sahaja Yogis do feel that I’m too compassionate

01:05:32.417 --> 01:05:35.458
and that I should be rather strict with people and things like that,

01:05:35.667 --> 01:05:38.375
you see, they come and tell Me some wisdom about it.

01:05:43.583 --> 01:05:46.291
You see they think I’m not so practical,

01:05:46.500 --> 01:05:49.750
but this is the most practical thing.

01:05:50.917 --> 01:05:53.625
Yes, I know they make mistakes

01:05:53.834 --> 01:05:55.667
because they don't know they are walking in darkness.

01:05:55.875 --> 01:05:58.208
If you are walking in darkness, you will bang at something.

01:05:58.417 --> 01:06:00.750
Then only thing you can do is to have compassion for them

01:06:00.959 --> 01:06:05.166
because they can’t see, they are blind. Isn’t it?

01:06:05.834 --> 01:06:09.542
How can you have any anger or temper?

01:06:19.834 --> 01:06:23.792
And moreover, I would request you not to have any misidentification

01:06:23.999 --> 01:06:25.500
with anyone whatsoever.

01:06:25.999 --> 01:06:29.000
You have to get to your Spirit, that’s the main thing.

01:06:29.583 --> 01:06:32.208
If you still think of somebody, you see,

01:06:32.417 --> 01:06:34.625
like the lady – I don’t know, somebody might have sent her here,

01:06:34.834 --> 01:06:36.625
maybe. I don’t know why she got angry.

01:06:36.834 --> 01:06:38.959
I didn’t say anything to hurt her.

01:06:39.750 --> 01:06:41.000
Maybe she is possessed.

01:06:41.208 --> 01:06:43.583
I don’t know why she has got angry with Me,

01:06:43.834 --> 01:06:45.750
and she just got up and just walked off saying that

01:06:45.999 --> 01:06:47.792
“You’re telling everything lies.”

01:06:50.208 --> 01:06:51.959
Why should I tell you lies?

01:06:52.125 --> 01:06:55.000
I don’t have to get anything out of you.

01:06:57.542 --> 01:07:00.542
But why it happens? Because she’s not sensitive,

01:07:00.834 --> 01:07:03.792
she’s not sensitive to Divinity.

01:07:05.417 --> 01:07:09.999
She doesn’t understand who’s Divine, who’s not. I don’t blame her.

01:07:10.583 --> 01:07:12.625
She hasn’t got the sensitivity. It’s a calibre.

01:07:12.875 --> 01:07:16.333
I have seen sahaja yogis now of different varieties have come to Me.

01:07:16.959 --> 01:07:19.458
Some of them are of such a calibre you can’t even believe.

01:07:19.709 --> 01:07:21.583
They get into realization, they know what it is,

01:07:21.792 --> 01:07:23.417
they have the pattern just like a diamond,

01:07:23.625 --> 01:07:24.917
they get it and they get into it.

01:07:25.166 --> 01:07:27.083
They’re tremendous people.

01:07:27.625 --> 01:07:30.208
There are some who slog behind.

01:07:30.417 --> 01:07:35.458
Some of them who get realization but still

01:07:35.792 --> 01:07:38.583
they go on doubting, all kinds.

01:07:39.041 --> 01:07:43.041
Doesn’t matter. I love all of them.

01:07:45.417 --> 01:07:46.417
Yes, My child?

01:08:03.999 --> 01:08:05.625
He is a sahaja yogi?

01:08:09.542 --> 01:08:11.333
So what is he talking now?

01:08:17.875 --> 01:08:18.834
What did he say?

01:08:19.000 --> 01:08:21.250
He's saying Mother, if before realization

01:08:21.458 --> 01:08:23.041
we were such a horrible person that

01:08:23.250 --> 01:08:27.458
we gave cancer to everybody we met or something like this,

01:08:27.834 --> 01:08:32.458
after realization does the effects of that get taken away

01:08:32.750 --> 01:08:34.000
or what happens?

01:08:34.208 --> 01:08:37.458
Yah. I know it, so many things have happened.

01:08:37.834 --> 01:08:40.792
We had somebody in Brighton, you remember –

01:08:41.166 --> 01:08:44.542
he’s here right now, I think –

01:08:44.834 --> 01:08:46.625
who was drunk when he came in.

01:08:46.999 --> 01:08:49.125
He was very angry with Me, you see, to begin with.

01:08:49.458 --> 01:08:50.959
He said, “How can I get rid of this trouble?

01:08:51.208 --> 01:08:53.000
I can’t believe You”, and all that.

01:08:53.375 --> 01:08:55.542
And he’s all right, perfectly all right.

01:08:55.834 --> 01:08:58.667
His change is so beautiful, you can’t… is he there?

01:08:58.875 --> 01:08:59.667
Yogi: Yes , I am.

01:08:59.999 --> 01:09:02.166
May God bless you.

01:09:05.999 --> 01:09:08.917
He’s so sweet now. The other day he came to see Me.

01:09:09.083 --> 01:09:13.083
I said, “Look at that. He’s so sweet.”

01:09:13.333 --> 01:09:16.375
He was a very sweet man, wasn’t he?

01:09:16.750 --> 01:09:21.208
But something had put him up, made him upset, you see,

01:09:21.875 --> 01:09:24.250
that he became alcoholic, you see.

01:09:24.542 --> 01:09:25.875
He’s all right.

01:09:26.291 --> 01:09:29.917
And the compassion can only make you understand this

01:09:30.625 --> 01:09:31.999
that there’s a reason for this –

01:09:32.333 --> 01:09:36.999
He is a very sweet person, very sweet person no doubt.

01:09:37.667 --> 01:09:39.667
But something had gone wrong with him.

01:09:40.208 --> 01:09:42.208
It’s all right.

01:09:44.792 --> 01:09:47.417
So this happens, it’s true.

01:09:47.625 --> 01:09:49.959
Sahaja yogis realize this.

01:09:50.208 --> 01:09:54.583
Some, of course, I must say, go little bit, doesn’t matter.

01:09:55.291 --> 01:09:57.125
They’ll come up, all of them will come up,

01:09:57.500 --> 01:09:59.999
I’m sure of it.

01:10:03.166 --> 01:10:06.333
Everyone is made for it.

01:10:06.917 --> 01:10:09.834
Actually, the Divine is anxious to give you realization –

01:10:10.208 --> 01:10:13.792
much more, much more anxious than you are.

01:10:14.375 --> 01:10:15.667
If there were thousand people today,

01:10:15.875 --> 01:10:18.291
I would have given them realization better.

01:10:18.959 --> 01:10:21.333
But very few people take to reality, you see now.

01:10:21.625 --> 01:10:26.875
That guru Maharaji, thousands are like mad after him, isn’t it?

01:10:27.542 --> 01:10:30.834
He’s given nothing to the poor people.

01:10:32.291 --> 01:10:35.999
But for reality, there are very few.

01:10:38.291 --> 01:10:40.667
Like the other day somebody asked Me a question,

01:10:40.917 --> 01:10:42.959
“Mother, why don’t You do it to everyone?”

01:10:43.125 --> 01:10:46.792
I said, “Where are they, everyone? They are missing.

01:10:47.375 --> 01:10:51.250
Where are they? In this Brighton, how many there are?

01:10:52.417 --> 01:10:54.125
How many are here?

01:10:54.500 --> 01:10:56.917
All right? That’s the problem.

01:10:57.500 --> 01:11:02.792
It takes time for people to love reality, time.

01:11:03.417 --> 01:11:06.458
It’s such a beautiful thing.

01:11:06.999 --> 01:11:09.709
And even they get realized, then they drop out, you see.

01:11:10.083 --> 01:11:11.917
They say, “Oh, I’m all right now. I’m all right.”

01:11:12.083 --> 01:11:14.542
After one year they’ll appear.

01:11:14.792 --> 01:11:15.917
That’s not the way.

01:11:16.500 --> 01:11:19.417
You have to master this art, absolutely master it.

01:11:19.750 --> 01:11:21.917
It is all free, absolutely free,

01:11:22.083 --> 01:11:26.625
now they are all sitting down here, they can say that.

01:11:28.625 --> 01:11:31.208
Would You talk a bit more about Self-realization and

01:11:31.458 --> 01:11:34.625
and, You know, what’s necessary to enhance that?

01:11:35.000 --> 01:11:39.959
Yes, Yes, I will be in My next lecture, one by one.

01:11:40.125 --> 01:11:42.625
Now I’m talking of the left side, the right side,

01:11:42.917 --> 01:11:46.208
and then the center, and then also, of course about the Spirit,

01:11:46.500 --> 01:11:49.166
definitely, hundred times, that’s what I have to do.

01:11:49.417 --> 01:11:52.250
But gradually I have to build you up. All right?

01:11:52.458 --> 01:11:55.291
I will definitely. You won’t believe,

01:11:56.709 --> 01:11:58.999
I think I have given five hundred lectures already

01:11:59.375 --> 01:12:01.375
in London, at least.

01:12:01.834 --> 01:12:03.250
And it doesn’t end. Every time they say,

01:12:03.458 --> 01:12:04.792
last time I spoke they said, "Mother,

01:12:04.999 --> 01:12:08.208
it was absolutely a new dimension You talked about”, you see.

01:12:08.458 --> 01:12:09.041
I don’t know.

01:12:09.250 --> 01:12:11.875
Kerry told Me first time he touched his vibrations so much

01:12:12.125 --> 01:12:15.999
with My lecture, I don’t know what I touched him so much.

01:12:16.333 --> 01:12:18.208
Yes, it’s surprising.

01:12:18.709 --> 01:12:20.166
He’s from Australia.

01:12:20.625 --> 01:12:23.083
Australians do well.

01:12:24.000 --> 01:12:25.417
Very fast work.

01:12:26.208 --> 01:12:29.125
So, all the questions are over now? Should we have it?

01:12:29.333 --> 01:12:31.083
What of Karma?

01:12:31.333 --> 01:12:32.750
Eh?

01:12:33.125 --> 01:12:38.041
Karma? Karmas are when you do any work

01:12:38.250 --> 01:12:43.333
or anything with your right side action

01:12:43.999 --> 01:12:48.750
then the effects of that accumulate within you as an ego

01:12:49.083 --> 01:12:50.375
because you think you are doing it.

01:12:50.583 --> 01:12:53.500
Actually, we don’t do anything substantial.

01:12:53.875 --> 01:12:54.999
What we do is a dead work.

01:12:55.166 --> 01:12:58.792
Like as I said we make a chair out of a dead, a tree.

01:12:58.999 --> 01:12:59.875
That’s all we do.

01:13:00.041 --> 01:13:02.709
What work we do is an idea we have we are doing work.

01:13:02.917 --> 01:13:04.041
What work are you doing?

01:13:04.250 --> 01:13:06.500
Can you convert this into a fruit?

01:13:06.959 --> 01:13:09.542
We can’t even put fragrance into it.

01:13:10.375 --> 01:13:13.250
So this myth, you see, works as ego within us

01:13:13.458 --> 01:13:16.500
as shown here, which I will be speaking tomorrow about, all right?

01:13:16.709 --> 01:13:19.375
And this is what is that we think we are doing this work,

01:13:19.583 --> 01:13:23.083
that work, and this ego thinks that

01:13:23.375 --> 01:13:27.500
if you have done bad work or good work we have to suffer.

01:13:28.083 --> 01:13:30.083
You see, a tiger doesn’t feel that way.

01:13:30.583 --> 01:13:33.583
If tiger has to eat, it must kill.

01:13:33.999 --> 01:13:36.667
It kills the animal, eats it, finished.

01:13:36.999 --> 01:13:40.208
It doesn’t sit down and sulk, “Oh, God, I should not have done it.

01:13:40.834 --> 01:13:44.834
I should become vegetarian.”

01:13:45.208 --> 01:13:50.667
It doesn’t accumulate any, any, any karmas in it, all right?

01:13:50.917 --> 01:13:52.542
But we human beings do. Why?

01:13:52.750 --> 01:13:54.458
Because we are closed.

01:13:54.750 --> 01:13:57.041
We are closed. See here, we are closed.

01:13:57.583 --> 01:13:58.667
They are open.

01:13:59.125 --> 01:14:01.000
Whatever they do, they are not bothered.

01:14:01.208 --> 01:14:05.709
But we are bothered about what we do because we think we do.

01:14:07.709 --> 01:14:14.041
And when, as I said, this center is opened out, He sucks our karmas,

01:14:14.333 --> 01:14:17.625
and the so-called karmas are nothing but sins, you see.

01:14:18.000 --> 01:14:21.166
In a biblical language we can call it as sin, you see.

01:14:21.625 --> 01:14:23.875
And they’re all sucked in

01:14:25.583 --> 01:14:30.625
by this powerful Deity of Christ awakened within us.

01:14:31.000 --> 01:14:34.542
And you get beyond it because it is the ego that does the karma.

01:14:34.792 --> 01:14:37.999
When your ego is finished, where there are the karmas?

01:14:38.333 --> 01:14:40.583
They are finished, too.

01:14:45.542 --> 01:14:47.750
Then you don’t say, “I did it.”

01:14:47.959 --> 01:14:49.083
What you will say,

01:14:49.291 --> 01:14:52.166
“Mother, it’s not working out, it’s not going up.”

01:14:52.375 --> 01:14:55.291
Now what is this 'it'? It becomes a third person.

01:14:55.500 --> 01:14:58.208
“It’s flowing. The vibrations are not coming.”

01:14:58.583 --> 01:15:01.834
You see, you don’t say, “I - I am doing this realization.

01:15:01.999 --> 01:15:04.750
I am raising the Kundalini”, they don’t say so.

01:15:04.999 --> 01:15:08.000
They say, “It’s not rising.”

01:15:08.250 --> 01:15:12.250
You become a third person. That third person is the Spirit.

01:15:12.875 --> 01:15:15.834
Where you do not say that “I should do it.”

01:15:16.208 --> 01:15:17.667
Even if it’s your son, you'll say,

01:15:17.875 --> 01:15:19.875
“Mother, it’s better he gets realization.”

01:15:20.083 --> 01:15:23.417
All right. You’ll see. Try. It doesn’t work out.

01:15:24.125 --> 01:15:26.625
All right, then should I give a certificate?

01:15:26.834 --> 01:15:29.291
He said, “How can You give certificate, Mother, how? Kundalini,

01:15:29.500 --> 01:15:32.291
Kundalini has not risen.” Everyone knows, you see,

01:15:32.500 --> 01:15:35.041
whether it’s your father, mother, sister - anyone –

01:15:35.250 --> 01:15:39.792
if they’re not realized, they know they’re not realized, so what?

01:15:39.999 --> 01:15:41.291
They just know.

01:15:42.999 --> 01:15:45.750
And this granddaughter of Mine, who was - she’s here now -

01:15:45.959 --> 01:15:47.291
she is a born realized,

01:15:47.500 --> 01:15:50.166
and she was hardly about five years of age, I think,

01:15:50.375 --> 01:15:51.959
when they went to Leach.

01:15:52.208 --> 01:15:53.333
And there was one lama sitting

01:15:53.542 --> 01:15:55.959
with a shaved head and all that, wearing and all that.

01:15:56.291 --> 01:15:58.166
Everybody was touching his feet.

01:15:58.458 --> 01:16:01.375
And the parents also, not realized, My daughter is not realized,

01:16:01.750 --> 01:16:02.792
so she also touched his feet.

01:16:02.999 --> 01:16:05.500
She couldn’t bear it anymore now, it was too much for her.

01:16:05.709 --> 01:16:08.000
She was sitting in a higher block.

01:16:08.208 --> 01:16:11.667
She went, put her hands back and looked at him, turning,

01:16:11.875 --> 01:16:14.166
She says, “What do you mean by asking everybody to touch your feet?

01:16:14.375 --> 01:16:16.999
You’re not even a realized soul!

01:16:18.250 --> 01:16:21.250
By wearing this dress of yours and shaving your head

01:16:21.417 --> 01:16:23.917
you think you can ask people to touch your feet?”

01:16:24.208 --> 01:16:28.583
Little child of five years, yet she understands.

01:16:29.333 --> 01:16:31.792
We had once a program in India

01:16:31.999 --> 01:16:34.000
when they invited Me as a chief guest and

01:16:34.208 --> 01:16:36.917
for this Raman worship - was a realized soul-

01:16:37.083 --> 01:16:40.250
and one gentleman from Ramkrishna ashram, the head of that,

01:16:40.458 --> 01:16:45.999
was sitting with his big orange robe, you see, sitting there.

01:16:46.375 --> 01:16:49.500
And My, another granddaughter, she was sitting in the front row.

01:16:50.166 --> 01:16:53.166
She couldn’t bear him anymore so she shouted from there,

01:16:53.375 --> 01:16:56.792
“Mother, the one whose wearing a maxi dress,

01:16:57.000 --> 01:16:58.458
Grandmother, please ask him to get out,

01:16:58.667 --> 01:17:00.041
he’s giving heat to all of us.”

01:17:00.250 --> 01:17:01.959
So you see, there were many sahaja yogis

01:17:02.125 --> 01:17:03.625
who were feeling the heat from the fellow

01:17:03.834 --> 01:17:05.458
and he thinks he’s a very Spiritual man.

01:17:05.667 --> 01:17:06.500
And she just stood up,

01:17:06.709 --> 01:17:09.125
she said, “Ask him to go, he is wearing a maxi.”

01:17:09.625 --> 01:17:11.458
She didn’t understand it was a robe or thing.

01:17:11.750 --> 01:17:13.667
Even children know

01:17:14.291 --> 01:17:16.208
who are realized souls and who are not,

01:17:16.875 --> 01:17:17.999
if they are born realized.

01:17:18.208 --> 01:17:20.166
There are many children who are born realized these days.

01:17:20.417 --> 01:17:24.709
The time of judgment, this is the time of judgment.

01:17:25.166 --> 01:17:27.291
Of course about this I’ll tell you later.

01:17:32.667 --> 01:17:34.709
Do You mind if I ask You a few questions?

01:17:35.750 --> 01:17:37.250
It’s all right, I don’t mind.

01:17:37.458 --> 01:17:39.291
But what happens, if you ask too many questions

01:17:39.500 --> 01:17:41.792
sometimes it becomes mental activity

01:17:41.999 --> 01:17:45.083
and may delay further realization sometimes.

01:17:45.333 --> 01:17:49.041
So I would advice you, if it is not so important, better keep it out

01:17:49.250 --> 01:17:52.583
because, you see, answering the question is only on mental level.

01:17:52.792 --> 01:17:54.875
I’m talking something much beyond, you see.

01:17:55.333 --> 01:17:59.041
So, it is something logically if you have understood Me -

01:17:59.250 --> 01:18:00.542
all right, let’s have it.

01:18:00.792 --> 01:18:02.166
If it will work out, work out.

01:18:02.375 --> 01:18:03.709
If it will not work out, doesn’t matter.

01:18:03.917 --> 01:18:06.959
I’m here for three-four days, and we are going to work it out.

01:18:07.750 --> 01:18:10.667
All right? So it’s better to keep your mind at rest.

01:18:10.875 --> 01:18:14.417
Tell the mind, “You have asked many questions before,

01:18:14.625 --> 01:18:19.333
you have thought of many things, now the time for you to receive

01:18:19.542 --> 01:18:23.959
the blessings of your own being.” All right?

01:18:24.333 --> 01:18:25.709
If you tell your mind, it will rest.

01:18:25.959 --> 01:18:29.125
It’s a, it’s a wonderful thing, mind is.

01:18:29.834 --> 01:18:33.208
If the mind knows what you want,

01:18:33.834 --> 01:18:38.250
and if it is the reality, it supports you and helps you very much.

01:18:38.458 --> 01:18:40.999
The same mind which can go astray, you see,

01:18:41.208 --> 01:18:43.583
it’s like sometimes like a donkey.

01:18:43.834 --> 01:18:49.458
Like Christ used donkey just to suggest the mind

01:18:49.667 --> 01:18:54.750
that if you allow it to go astray

01:18:54.959 --> 01:18:56.583
it will take you to all kinds of things,

01:18:56.792 --> 01:19:01.625
but if you control it, it takes you there where you have to go.

01:19:02.709 --> 01:19:05.166
You just make him keep quiet.

01:19:05.375 --> 01:19:07.999
It’s better to keep quiet at mind level.

01:19:08.500 --> 01:19:10.583
And that’s why I answered your questions

01:19:10.875 --> 01:19:13.500
because later on when the Kundalini’s rising,

01:19:13.709 --> 01:19:16.083
at that time, the mind should not stand up, isn’t it,

01:19:16.291 --> 01:19:18.834
to say that “I haven’t asked this question.” That’s why.

01:19:19.000 --> 01:19:21.000
Just to soothe it – there’s no need –

01:19:21.208 --> 01:19:24.667
but, just to soothe it down, I do it. All right?

01:19:24.999 --> 01:19:27.125
So best thing is to get your realization is the best thing,

01:19:27.333 --> 01:19:29.959
otherwise this mind is quite a disturbing stuff.

01:19:30.333 --> 01:19:31.792
It can come at the right time,

01:19:31.999 --> 01:19:36.583
when you are going to achieve your last breakthrough, it may stop.

01:19:36.834 --> 01:19:37.625
All right?

01:19:37.834 --> 01:19:39.750
So if you have any immediate question

01:19:39.959 --> 01:19:42.542
by which you are really oppressed  then you must ask Me.

01:19:42.750 --> 01:19:44.583
But if it is not so important, just give up.

01:19:45.125 --> 01:19:46.417
Is it very important?

01:19:46.875 --> 01:19:50.709
Then it’s all right. He has realized it.

01:19:50.999 --> 01:19:56.083
Now, I have to just request you one thing, if you don't mind,

01:19:56.291 --> 01:19:57.667
we have to take out our shoes,

01:19:57.875 --> 01:20:00.291
because the mother earth has such a lot, you see,

01:20:00.500 --> 01:20:03.291
so we have to take her help in every way possible.
